            <title>[WFCORE-51] Improve error message for bad/incomplete XML in deployment scanner</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFCORE-51</link>
                <project id="12315422" key="WFCORE">WildFly Core</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Deploying VDB with invalid XML (closed translator tag). Causes following error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;org.jboss.as.server.deployment.scanner&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (DeploymentScanner-threads - 1)  JBAS015009: Scan found incompletely copied file content for deployment standalone/deployments/loop-vdb.xml. Deployment changes will not be processed until all content is complete.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
